Package com.github.ignition.location.utils

Class Summary
FroyoLocationUpdateRequester Provides support for initiating active and passive location updates optimized for the Froyo release.
GingerbreadLocationUpdateRequester Provides support for initiating active and passive location updates optimized for the Gingerbread release.
IgnitedGingerbreadLastLocationFinder Optimized implementation of Last Location Finder for devices running Gingerbread and above.
IgnitedLegacyLastLocationFinder Legacy implementation of Last Location Finder for all Android platforms down to Android 1.6.
IgnitedLocationSupport  
LegacyLocationUpdateRequester Provides support for initiating active and passive location updates for all Android platforms from Android 1.6.
